<resources>
    <!--
    STUDIO GHIBLI-INSPIRED COLOR PALETTE
    
    Inspired by the warm, natural, and dreamy aesthetics of
    Studio Ghibli films like Spirited Away, My Neighbor Totoro,
    and Howl's Moving Castle.
    
    Features:
    - Soft, muted tones instead of harsh saturated colors
    - Warm earth tones and sky blues
    - Nature-inspired greens and gentle sunset oranges
    -->

